	<string name="_bx_chat_plus_information_block"><![CDATA[To enable this module, chat server must be installed separately. <br />

Enter the chat URL in this module settings. <br />

Then OAuth login must be configured. <a href="{0}modules/?r=oauth2/administration/">Generate Key & Secret pair</a> in OAuth2 Server module by pointing chat URL and  desired name. <br />

After Key & Secret pair is generated you need to enter them in Chat Administration &gt; OAuth &gt; Trident.

<hr />

To enable Helpdesk Chat you need to enable it in the Chat Administration &gt; Livechat and in this module settings. You don't need to insert JS code, it is added automatically.]]></string>
